次咁辛苦做咁多野，到頭嚟都係要比人屌<br />\n既然係咁，<br />\n大家係咪時候諗下要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直搗皇龍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔關政見問題，係有的確為所不少既人只關注生計<br />\n同有冇屋企番，甚至會主動清road block<br />\n即使唔係撐警<br />\n既然守中大又要送頭，守旺角又要通頂<br />\n但係都迫唔到政府做啲乜<br />\n我就眼白白見住手足啲血係腳邊流<br />\n<br />\n4個月喇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解宜家仲唔升級去搞啲官</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n至少仲會多人支持<br />\n<br />\n策略：小隊突擊，人在明我在暗<br />\n<br />\n要救中大/所有人就要有大啲話語權，宜家有話語權既係官"},{"pid":"834073fdfc6bedc860e246b4e877f0796d51b473","tid":1714474,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"你覺得依家係玩？"},{"pid":"ea6799939e9a0c9ae2fab7b10d5be94f1b745126","tid":1714474,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:40:18.000Z","msg":"11.14 曙光行動 繼續三罷<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/evpMOT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/evpMOT</a>"},{"pid":"c656421cff1923506acc99ab749c124161e95aa3","tid":1714474,"uid":2984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:40:31.000Z","msg":"玩你老母，識唔識用字"},{"pid":"85fd0680ed20af75b8b1400545f3ff0fefd53751","tid":1714474,"uid":56546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c656421cff1923506acc99ab749c124161e95aa3","tid":1714474,"uid":2984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:40:31.000Z","msg":"玩你老母，識唔識用字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:44:20.000Z","msg":"就係要同佢玩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n年青人最大強項就係玩嘢<br />\n要玩死政府, 玩死差佬<br />\n今次要用我地優勢打沉敵人"},{"pid":"32c602133df98c30339ac6c20adf45a56eec2b82","tid":1714474,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:46:31.000Z","msg":"啱啱有線財經分析 個分析員話癱瘓中環係有影響 好多外國人唔知道乜嘢係沙田乜嘢深水埗淨係知道中環"},{"pid":"4f08e8dc0998efa551b6a7d3c8ecf2ce7ed5867b","tid":1714474,"uid":136317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"今日咪又係開到市